# ─── Cycle.gg environment ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Server-side Riot API key. Never prefixed with VITE_ so it stays server-
# only and never gets bundled into the browser. Both the Vite dev proxy
# and the production Vercel Edge Function read this same variable.
#
# Get a key at https://developer.riotgames.com:
#   - "Development API Key" (rotates every 24h — fine for testing)
#   - "Personal API Key" (permanent, ~48h approval — needed for prod)
#
# For production: set it on Vercel instead of committing it here.
#   vercel env add RIOT_API_KEY production
#
# RIOT_API_KEY=RGAPI-xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
